=NexusGate's best customers are:
- Phone-dependent businesses (roofing, HVAC, plumbing, dental, law, real estate)
- Owner-operated or small team businesses (1–30 staff)
- Businesses with real job values ($300–$5,000+ per job or client)
- Businesses with no after-hours coverage or an overwhelmed front desk
- Located in DC, Maryland, or Virginia

Score this lead from 0–10 based on ICP fit:

Business name: {{ $json.business_name }}
Business type: {{ $json.business_type }}
City: {{ $json.city }}
Google rating: {{ $json.google_rating }}
Review count: {{ $json.review_count }}
Website: {{ $json.website }}

Return ONLY valid JSON:
{
  "score": <integer 0-10>,
  "reasoning": "<1-2 sentences>",
  "pain_point": "<the most likely pain this business has with missed calls>",
  "personalization_hook": "<one specific detail to open the cold email with>"
}

